ORG &O50000
SADD &O50000
JP MAIN

; I/O Subroutines

>EXFWD DATA 0
>EXFAL DATA 0
STRAL EXFWD
EXF 0
DATA EXFWD
DATA EXFWD
SKPFIN 0
JP LOK-1
IJP EXFAL

>OUTWD DATA 0
>OUTAL DATA 0
STRAL OUTWD
OUT 0
DATA OUTWD
DATA OUTWD
SKPOIN 0
JP LOK-1
IJP OUTAL

; Outputs "HI\r\n" and halts
>MAIN SIL 0
ENTSR 0
ENTALK &O13
RJP EXFAL
ENTALK &O110
RJP OUTAL
ENTALK &O111
RJP OUTAL
ENTALK &O15
RJP OUTAL
ENTALK &O12
RJP OUTAL
>DONE JP DONE
END
